Package org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.exec.vector.keyseries

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    VectorKeySeries
    An abstraction of keys within a VectorizedRowBatch.
    VectorKeySeriesSerialized
    An abstract adding serialization to key series.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    VectorKeySeriesBytesSerialized<T extends SerializeWrite>
    A key series of a single column of byte array keys where the keys get serialized.
    VectorKeySeriesImpl
    A base implementation of VectorKeySeries.
    VectorKeySeriesLongSerialized<T extends SerializeWrite>
    A key series of a single column of long keys where the keys get serialized.
    VectorKeySeriesMultiSerialized<T extends SerializeWrite>
    A key series of a multiple columns of keys where the keys get serialized.
    VectorKeySeriesSerializedImpl<T extends SerializeWrite>
    Implementation of base serialization interface.
    VectorKeySeriesSingleImpl
    Implementation of when a one key series or a serialized key series is being presented.
